casebody.head_matter:
S.D., a Minor, By His Parents and Natural Guardians, A.D. and R.D., et al., petitioners,

HADDON HEIGHTS BOARD OF EDUCATION.
No. 16-1054.

On petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit. Petition for writ of certiorari granted.
